headline.main: Athletics: Harrison and Baker Speed to Yearly Bests in U.S. Champs
headline.print_headline: Athletics: Harrison and Baker Speed to Yearly Bests in U.S. Champs

lead_paragraph: Top hurdler Keni Harrison and up-and-coming sprinter Ronnie Baker ran the fastest times in the world this year at the U.S. indoor championships in Albuquerque, New Mexico on Sunday.
